The following functionality will be implemented with future versions, if needed:

Background tasks: automatic indexing, checking of hosts, checking of current watchers
Automatic CDLC download from supported websites into pre-configured folder
Fallback implementation for CDLC search (similar to the original bot, querying the website)
Sub & mod support
Improve queue by managing already played more explicitly

BEFORE RELEASE
    Document all commands in README
COMMANDS
    FLWR
        !played - list of picked songs that were next'd
    VWR
        !joke - best joke
        !last - last next'd
        !playlist - request queue (no more than TOP 5)
        !commands - list of public commands available to your rank
        !hosts - list of hosts for the channel

Type hint review (customsforge, others)

Launch link in browser after !next
